{"type":"message","id":"1b8d5332","parentId":"37a078e5","timestamp":"2026-03-31T23:09:48.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ÁĒ®śą∑ťóģÁöĄśėĮŚ¶āšĹēŤé∑ŚŹĖ Firecrawl Search ÁöĄ API„ÄāśąĎťúÄŤ¶Āśü•Áúč firecrawl skill śĚ•šļÜŤß£ŚÖ∑šĹďÁöĄťÖćÁĹģśĖĻś≥ē„Äā\n\nŤģ©śąĎŚÖąŤĮĽŚŹĖ firecrawl skill śĖášĽ∂„Äā","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fe19099b607b45db9ef9fec1","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"~/.openclaw/skills/firecrawl-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":24087,"output":88,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774998582980,"responseId":"0e0771ad8a81ebf6b29a92ab87c8fb5b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5e7382d","parentId":"1b8d5332","timestamp":"2026-03-31T23:09:48.798Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fe19099b607b45db9ef9fec1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: firecrawl\ndescription: Web search and scraping via Firecrawl API. Use when you need to search the web, scrape websites (including JS-heavy pages), crawl entire sites, or extract structured data from web pages. Requires FIRECRAWL_API_KEY environment variable.\n---\n\n# Firecrawl\n\nWeb search and scraping via Firecrawl API.\n\n## Prerequisites\n\nSet `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY` in your environment or `.env` file:\n```bash\nexport FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=fc-xxxxxxxxxx\n```\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Search the web\n```bash\nfirecrawl_search \"your search query\" --limit 10\n```\n\n### Scrape a single page\n```bash\nfirecrawl_scrape \"https://example.com\"\n```\n\n### Crawl an entire site\n```bash\nfirecrawl_crawl \"https://example.com\" --max-pages 50\n```\n\n## API Reference\n\nSee [references/api.md](references/api.md) for detailed API documentation and advanced options.\n\n## Scripts\n\n- `scripts/search.py` - Search the web with Firecrawl\n- `scripts/scrape.py` - Scrape a single URL\n- `scripts/crawl.py` - Crawl an entire website\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774998588791}}
{"type":"message","id":"d39dfcc0","parentId":"d5e7382d","timestamp":"2026-03-31T23:10:00.345Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ÁĒ®śą∑śÉ≥Áü•ťĀďŚ¶āšĹēŤé∑ŚŹĖ Firecrawl API key„ÄāśąĎťúÄŤ¶ĀŚĎäŤĮČšĽĖś≥®ŚÜĆśĶĀÁ®č„ÄāŤģ©śąĎśźúÁīĘšłÄšłč Firecrawl ŚģėÁĹĎšŅ°śĀĮ„Äā","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Ťé∑ŚŹĖ Firecrawl API Key ÁöĄś≠•ť™§Ôľö\n\n### 1ÔłŹ‚É£ ś≥®ŚÜĆŤī¶ŚŹ∑\nŤģŅťóģ Firecrawl ŚģėÁĹĎÔľö**https://www.firecrawl.dev/**\n\nÁāĻŚáĽŚŹ≥šłäŤßí **\"Sign Up\"** śąĖ **\"Get Started\"**ÔľĆŚŹĮšĽ•šĹŅÁĒ® GitHub śąĖ Google Ťī¶ŚŹ∑ŚŅęťÄüś≥®ŚÜĆ„Äā\n\n### 2ÔłŹ‚É£ Ťé∑ŚŹĖ API Key\nś≥®ŚÜĆÁôĽŚĹēŚźéÔľö\n1. ŤŅõŚÖ• **Dashboard** śéßŚą∂ŚŹį\n2. śČĺŚąį **API Keys** ťÉ®ŚąÜ\n3. Ś§ćŚą∂šĹ†ÁöĄ API KeyÔľąś†ľŚľŹÔľö`fc-xxxxxxxxxx`ÔľČ\n\n### 3ÔłŹ‚É£ ťÖćÁĹģŚąį OpenClaw\nŚú® OpenClaw šł≠ŤģĺÁĹģÁéĮŚĘÉŚŹėťáŹÔľö\n\n**śĖĻś≥ēšłÄÔľöšłīśó∂ŤģĺÁĹģ**\n```bash\nexport FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=fc-šĹ†ÁöĄŚĮÜťí•\n```\n\n**śĖĻś≥ēšļĆÔľöŚÜôŚÖ•ťÖćÁĹģśĖášĽ∂Ôľąśé®ŤćźÔľČ**\nÁľĖŤĺĎ `~/.openclaw/.env` śĖášĽ∂ÔľĆś∑ĽŚä†Ôľö\n```\nFIRECRAWL_API_KEY=fc-šĹ†ÁöĄŚĮÜťí•\n```\n\n### ūüíį ŚÖćŤīĻťĘĚŚļ¶\nFirecrawl śŹźšĺõ **500 ś¨°/śúą** ŚÖćŤīĻŤįÉÁĒ®ťĘĚŚļ¶ÔľĆŤ∂≥Ś§üśó•ŚłłšĹŅÁĒ®„Äā\n\n---\n\nťúÄŤ¶ĀśąĎŚłģšĹ†ťÖćÁĹģŚźóÔľüśčŅŚąį API Key ŚźéŚĎäŤĮČśąĎŚć≥ŚŹĮ„Äā"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-43-133-33-215-3000","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":24402,"output":303,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24705,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774998588801,"responseId":"a5561d9619db2eacb99c75e40b5e2424"}}
